-- Mitsubishi Electric Increases Budget for Capital Expenditures, Nikkei Says
-- B y   S t e v e n   M c P h e r s o n
-- 2010-12-13T23:53:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-13/mitsubishi-electric-increases-budget-for-capital-expenditures-nikkei-says.html
Mitsubishi Electric Corp.’s capital
spending will reach 185 billion yen ($2.2 billion) in the fiscal
year ending March 31, 35 billion yen above the company’s plan,
the Nikkei newspaper reported. Mitsubishi increased production
of power semiconductors and conducted tests of smart grid power
distribution, according to the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven McPherson at 
 smcpherson@bloomberg.net  